{"code":"8t","title":"Testimonies for the Church, vol. 8","author":"Ellen G. White","chapters":[{"number":8,"title":"Warnings and Counsels Given to the Battle","content":"Creek Church . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 52 The time of the End . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 53 Help in Time of Trouble . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 54 A Failure to Honor God . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 54 Chapter 9--Our Duty to the World . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 57 How to Gain Success . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 58 Chapter 10--Missionary Work at Home and Abroad . . . . . . 60 An Illustration of the Work We Are to Do . . . . . . . . . . . . . 60 A Neglected Work . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 62 Chapter 11--The Holy Spirit in our Schools . . . . . . . . . . . . . 64 The Will of God Concerning Us . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 65 Working Against the Holy Spirit . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 67 Chapter 12--A Departure from Right . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 69 Chapter 13--Look to God for Help . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 71 Medical Missionary Work . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 72 A Word of Caution . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 75 Chapter 14--An Appeal to the Brethren in Battle Creek . . . . 77 Chapter 15--A Neglected Warning . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 82 Chapter 16--The Result of Reformation . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 87 Chapter 17--A Solemn Warning . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 90 Chapter 18--The Review and Herald Fire . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 96\n\niii\n\nChapter 19--What Might Have Been . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 102 Chapter 20--Forgetfulness . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 105\n\nA Hymn Of The Promised Land . . . .